The paper describes a deep reinforcement learning algorithm and its application to robotics tasks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). Among these, machine learning and robotics are the most likely categories, as the paper focuses on a deep RL algorithm and its application to robotics tasks. Artificial intelligence is also likely, as the paper discusses the challenges and limitations of RL algorithms in real-world domains. Systems and control and computer vision and pattern recognition are less likely, as they are not as directly related to the paper's main contributions.
